{
  "id": "2652460696_1",
  "title": "多名老师血铅也严重超标！“幼儿园铅中毒事件”最新后续",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content autoTypeSetting24psection\" id=\"js_content\">\n <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mctqt3jv16nz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 165, 235);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n    澎湃新闻记者 胥辉 廖艳\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   甘肃天水褐石培心幼儿园儿童被检出血铅超标后，多名幼儿园老师经检测，血铅也严重超标。此前，据该幼儿园的老师讲，平日她们与孩子们在幼儿园内同吃同住。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe videosnap_video_iframe\" data-authiconurl=\"http://dldir1.qq.com/weixin/checkresupdate/internet_news_media_auth_icon_38887ee9f6fe4639904638b28745b3f8.png\" data-desc=\"#天水褐石培心幼儿园铅中毒事件追踪：多名老师血铅也严重超标，“与孩子们在幼儿园内同吃同住，有头晕、恶心的症状以为是生理期反应”，天水医院设血铅异常门诊，有家长要求检测被拒\" data-headimgurl=\"http://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/0nn3FBrD9a3p8JkxgttfvRKI2pt1RkOYx7icX9wtR2Xap8n4Tdoib3pg/0\" data-height=\"1920\" data-id=\"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAA1G8GpBxwlgAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPEkYJMKnAsMZyIzNPgMIsmv_7Aith4z04VNzoiCDFi\" data-nickname=\"澎湃新闻\" data-nonceid=\"6432667941529007514\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-type=\"video\" data-url=\"https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=oibeqyX228riaCwo9STVsGLPj9UYCicgttvM5h9YDT5Z36sE2uu51rgIgBtmLibfvJ3WiaDsMeKGgZGmRaibQj2zmK1Pic6ahtxUPMbKHZCMdogia7GaJcuEDIgn4IrUmnyAnnWibvlqwJZ5bvQU&amp;token=ic1n0xDG6aw8AlbsUvic476pykTqkwMAlCw2ECyhr5bWSmnM4ibcaMBzu1qDpwWLChMulibNGXWMKzIHwfeYMTFKKEZ4IRQF2KmWngkVdzQwhUhZjvnE7gCwBVjomLvWriaqyleCt6VjjcOGaIVT0iaKH5st7FXq9e97eZzmNOEMwLxq0&amp;idx=1&amp;hy=SH&amp;m=33d98151805d283ecfcf7f8e4e7d9824&amp;uzid=1\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c7e48d19c0d4c90ce533b0772e1c08f4c6e0ce38be3ca98f63f23589@finder\" data-width=\"1080\">\n  </mp-common-videosnap>\n </section>\n <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   7月7日深夜，天水市褐石培心幼儿园一名老师的家属告诉澎湃新闻，幼儿园多名老师的检测报告陆续出炉，已知两位老师检测结果：一人为395ug/L，另一位则超500ug/L。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   随后，该幼儿园老师王丽发来她的检验报告单显示，其血铅数值为395μg/L（微克每升），而成人血铅正常参考值应该是200μg/L（微克每升）。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   一位在西安市中心医院的幼儿家长随后也证实了这一消息，称下午\n   <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n    多名老师在该院拿到血铅超标的检测结果，均显示超标。\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section>\n  <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mctqtip71q05\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"1279\" data-imgfileid=\"504976998\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" data-width=\"1706\" height=\"1279\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3S8WBk1dhWNGUzY684kIu6KLNQvSVCWGDBtILcbibvqqmZ1WnnZYj6nBU4T4zB3xU8Nt1tkgzd05jRQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"max-width: 1080px;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" width=\"1706\"/>\n   </span>\n   <span mpa-font-style=\"mctqtiorezq\" style=\"color: #888888;font-size: 14px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     西安市中心医院的住院证上已明确为“铅中毒”。本文图片均为澎湃新闻记者 胥辉 图\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mctqtmow7fl\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mctqtmoj15m7\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <strong style=\"\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 165, 235);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     多名老师跨省检测，\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </p>\n <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mctqtmow7fl\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mctqtmoj15m7\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 18px;\">\n  <strong style=\"\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 165, 235);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     确诊血铅超标\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   天水市褐石培心幼儿园老师林心7日晚上告诉澎湃新闻，7月1日，她参加了学校统一组织安排的血铅检测，但结果尚不清楚。今日，她又到医院重新做了一次血铅检测，现在也还没有出结果。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <figure domtype=\"img\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"886\" data-imgfileid=\"504977001\" data-ratio=\"0.7099358974358975\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1248\" data-width=\"1248\" height=\"886\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/yl6JkZAE3S8WBk1dhWNGUzY684kIu6KLW86tSLBziabCFXibBliaRUu4wzPdIVmLuOMmicOQ8vAEDVNqpIDyseIxwQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"max-width: 1080px;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" width=\"1248\"/>\n  </span>\n  <figcaption data-placeholder=\"请输入图片描述（最多五十字）\">\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   7日晚上，褐石培心幼儿园另一名老师王丽告诉澎湃新闻，7日下午，她收到了西安市中心医院出具的血铅检测单，数据显示血铅值为395ug/L。甘肃天水市政府相关部门向他们表示，针对此次血铅异常事件，他们在天水市设立了专门的专家医生团队，对血铅异常的老师们，进行专业治疗。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   王丽说，目前她还是有恶心的症状。大约在半个月前，她出现过头晕、恶心的症状，身边也有个别同事有类似反应，不过大家都没有过于关注，以为是生理期反应。据她了解，其他老师的检测结果也比较高，但具体多少不清楚。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   王丽表示，事发至今，当地有关部门没有向她们说明具体是什么添加剂导致中毒，她打算明天先去医院看看情况。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   7月7日下午，在陕西西安市中心医院带孩子就诊的一位家长证实，下午多名老师在该院拿到血铅检测结果，均严重超标。来自甘肃天水的相关部门工作人员在现场动员，希望老师们回天水治疗。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <strong>\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 165, 235);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     探访四家幼儿园，\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 18px;\">\n  <strong>\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 165, 235);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     其中三家正常开园\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   7月7日，星期一。澎湃新闻实地探访甘肃省天水褐石培心幼儿园三所关联幼儿园——蒙迪爱幼儿园、渭北幼儿园、慈爱幼儿园——均正常开园。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   此前一天，有家长反馈，目前已出的检测报告中，尚未发现这三所幼儿园的孩子血铅异常情况。而褐石培心幼儿园大多孩子已因血铅数据异常，住进了西安市中心医院，住院证上明确诊断为“铅中毒”。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section>\n  <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mctr7cwzzrb\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 16px;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"695\" data-imgfileid=\"504977000\" data-ratio=\"0.695\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" data-width=\"1000\" height=\"695\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3S8WBk1dhWNGUzY684kIu6KL0giaSsjqfOUE40ibsJuQNLkgtn3027XW4Lu3GIZId6o5zuwWaiafXlAaQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"max-width: 1080px;height: auto;display: block;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;\" width=\"1000\"/>\n   </span>\n   <span mpa-font-style=\"mctr7cwj178f\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     褐石培心幼儿园\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   一位此前在褐石培心幼儿园，现已升入小学一年级的幼儿家长称，女儿的两位同学血铅检测结果分别为114ug/L（血铅的正常值在0-100ug/L之间）、110.54ug/L，她的女儿为83.13ug/L，这个结果让她略感宽慰，当日带着孩子回到了天水。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   7月7日上午，蒙迪爱幼儿园内传来了孩子们的欢笑声，正常开园未见异常；在渭北幼儿园上学的一名幼儿家长称，该幼儿园周一正常开园，不过幼儿园一早通知，当地从一家其他幼儿园抽调了厨师过来。该家长称，4日，有警察带走了幼儿园的厨师，可能是协助调查。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <figure data-mpa-action-id=\"mctr5fmyqrn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" domtype=\"img\">\n  <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mctr584j13do\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"747\" data-imgfileid=\"504976997\" data-ratio=\"0.747\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" data-width=\"1000\" height=\"747\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3S8WBk1dhWNGUzY684kIu6KLibCtf6YhHBqYfkRia2KZO4UH8NwF49L55EsmN2pcpI72I958W2O0eaDw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"max-width: 1080px;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" width=\"1000\"/>\n  </span>\n  <span mpa-font-style=\"mctr5fmij0q\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n   <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mctr5fmi1jxk\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" leaf=\"\" style=\"\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     渭北幼儿园\n    </span>\n   </span>\n   <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mctr5fmim6s\" leaf=\"\" style=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </figure>\n <figure domtype=\"img\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </figure>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   此前，天水方面召集褐石培心幼儿园的家长开过一次通报会，会上曾透露初判系三色枣发糕和玉米肠卷添加剂超标。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   渭北幼儿园一位家长提供的幼儿园班级群此前公布的食谱信息显示，里面没有三色枣发糕，仅在去年11月份、今年2月份和4月份，有三天的早餐中出现过玉米卷肠。此外，去年11月和今年6月，红糖发糕曾在早餐中出现过两次。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   这是否意味着渭北幼儿园、褐石培心幼儿园，这两家同一实际控制人、距离只有1000多米的幼儿园并未统一采购食品？澎湃新闻多次咨询两家幼儿园教职工，未得到回应。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   蒙迪爱幼儿园一位家长告诉澎湃新闻，四家幼儿园都由实际控制人李慧芳担任园长，李慧芳经常站在门口迎接孩子，看上去和蔼可亲。但出事之后，李慧芳没再出现过。澎湃新闻探访发现，李慧芳控制的另一家慈爱幼儿园也正常开园。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   7月6日，澎湃新闻记者实地探访位于天水市麦积区的褐石培心幼儿园，该园有三层楼，大门临街，后侧操场铺设塑胶地板、儿童游乐设施，与褐石公馆小区仅隔着铁栅栏。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   澎湃新闻注意到，幼儿园门口张贴的“麦积区幼儿园责任督学公告”中，首项督导内容即为安全管理情况。拨打公告督导工作人员电话，接通后即被挂断，短信未获回复。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   附近商户及居民反映，近期幼儿园因部分幼儿血铅异常引发关注，事发后来了多辆警车、救护车，还有工人曾在门口下水道进行挖掘作业，不确定是否在采样。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <figure domtype=\"img\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 16px;\">\n  <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mcts1zl94b6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mcts1zl71uor\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"750\" data-imgfileid=\"504976999\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" data-width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3S8WBk1dhWNGUzY684kIu6KLZvtZJ6zPfeLgHYgibOm4UciaGVm0GLiatOaFPUmcySAwzmDqrP9lX2qPg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"max-width: 1080px;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" width=\"1000\"/>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n    蒙迪爱幼儿园\n   </span>\n  </span>\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </figure>\n <figure domtype=\"img\">\n  <figcaption>\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <section>\n  <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mcts28hn1tbd\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 16px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"750\" data-imgfileid=\"504977003\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" data-width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3S8WBk1dhWNGUzY684kIu6KLYtsZlnQ1dnKgBJJKO0ibDIiaPotjB92EaKj6v7DWYbxIYuDcibgJZVykg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"max-width: 1080px;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" width=\"1000\"/>\n   </span>\n   <span mpa-font-style=\"mcts28hewfd\" style=\"color: #888888;font-size: 14px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     慈爱幼儿园\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <strong data-mpa-action-id=\"mctr87lf1ji9\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 165, 235);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     天水医院设血铅异常门诊，\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <strong data-mpa-action-id=\"mctr87lfq6s\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 165, 235);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     有家长要求检测被拒\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   7月7日，不少带孩子在陕西西安市医疗机构做检验的家长拿到了检验单，确认铅超标的大都是褐石培心幼儿园的孩子。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   渭北幼儿园几位家长刚拿到在西安医疗机构给孩子检测的结果，“几个娃娃的都是7.0ug/L，和之前天水检测一样”。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   7月6日22时，天水市第二人民医院（天水二医院）《通知》：为进一步满足市民对儿童血铅异常预防及治疗专业知识的咨询需求，天水市第二人民医院积极行动，特开设血铅异常咨询门诊、儿科咨询门诊、心理咨询门诊，并邀请国家、省、市级专家坐诊，为市民提供专业诊疗服务。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <figure domtype=\"img\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"750\" data-imgfileid=\"504977002\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" data-width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3S8WBk1dhWNGUzY684kIu6KLLktUsoSrZeYMT4eCJ1HNs15ib1WfQJeh0QavhOchaQU64WgviczVXWYQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"max-width: 1080px;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" width=\"1000\"/>\n  </span>\n  <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mcts2pqsjfo\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mcts2pqqref\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 14px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n    天水第二人民医院\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </figure>\n <figure domtype=\"img\">\n  <figcaption>\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <figure data-mpa-action-id=\"mctrjmqm1a40\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" domtype=\"img\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"785\" data-imgfileid=\"504977004\" data-ratio=\"0.785\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" data-width=\"1000\" height=\"785\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3S8WBk1dhWNGUzY684kIu6KLMJJKjab0kerQBD45qhtK8Csdyib9siaYicfV9UZ4ibI2KYjGlfoGhvKQUg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"max-width: 1080px;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" width=\"1000\"/>\n  </span>\n  <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mcts2k1o243e\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mcts2k1m20mo\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 14px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n    天水第二医院设立了血铅异常咨询门诊。\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </figure>\n <figure domtype=\"img\">\n  <figcaption>\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   通知称，此次专家团队阵容强大，涵盖多领域专业人才。中国疾病预防控制中心中毒控制首席专家孙承业领衔，白银市第一人民医院职业病科主任医师孙德兴、甘肃省人民医院急诊科主任医师陈红纲、甘肃省妇幼保健院儿童保健科副主任医师朱瑛等，将凭借丰富经验为儿童血铅异常相关问题提供专业解答与诊疗建议。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   7月7日上午10时许，澎湃新闻在天水二医院门诊楼三楼儿科门诊咨询点看到，前来咨询的家长和儿童不多。一位老人正带着一名女童要求做血铅检测，但被医务人员告知，只有李慧芳园长名下四家幼儿园的孩子、此前集中检测时漏检的才可以检测，其余幼儿园的孩子不接收。当老人表示要自费检测时，医生亦表示“也不行”。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   这位医生明确告诉澎湃新闻，如果不是这四家幼儿园的孩子，可以去周边的白银市人民医院，天水查不了。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   但澎湃新闻半小时后电话咨询天水二医院，却被告知可以正常检测血铅，并未只针对“四所幼儿园”进行检测。为何如此？其中缘由暂时不得而知。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mctrjt2q1sj1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mctrjt2i24ie\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 14px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\" style=\"\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n    （林心、王丽均为化名）\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section data-pm-slice=\"8 14 []\" style='padding: 0px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", 黑体, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);pointer-events: initial;'>\n  <section style='margin: 0px;padding: 0px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", 黑体, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);pointer-events: initial;'>\n   <section style='padding: 0px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", 黑体, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);pointer-events: initial;'>\n    <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <section style='margin: 0px;padding: 0px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", 黑体, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);pointer-events: initial;'>\n      <span style=\"padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;pointer-events: initial;\">\n       <section data-pm-slice='2 2 [\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"section\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"padding: 0px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(53, 53, 53);font-family: \\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", \\\"Hiragino Sans GB\\\", \\\"Microsoft YaHei\\\", 黑体, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);pointer-events: initial;\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"section\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"line-height: 1.75em;\"},\"namespaceURI\":\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"},\"para\",{\"tagName\":\"section\",\"attributes\":{\"style\":\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 10